lead_paragraph: FIFA has charged the Irish Football Association (FAI) over a shirt logo worn in March to commemorate the 100th anniversary of an uprising against British rule.

headline.print_headline: FIFA Charge Irish FA Over 1916 Easter Uprising Logo
